tool_description: With these APIs you can easily get all the data you need. For example, you can have the logo in various formats through make, search for all cars of a certain make, model, ECU or engine. You can get complete data like make, model, ECU, engine, horsepower, engine size, fuel type and much more.  If you are looking for a constantly updated and complete API, this is for you
name: Cars Data
title: Cars Data

api_list.name: /getMakes
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://cars-data2.p.rapidapi.com/get/getMakes"

headers = {
            "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "cars-data2.p.rapidapi.com"
        }

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)
print(response.json())

api_list.name: /getECU/
api_list.description:
Get all ECUs from a specified make,  model , generation and engine
(You can use query parameters or body parameters example : 
getModels/Audi 
getModels?make=Audi
)
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://cars-data2.p.rapidapi.com/get/getECU/Alfa Romeo/147/2001-2005/1.6 T-Spark 105hp"

headers = {
            "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "cars-data2.p.rapidapi.com"
        }

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)
print(response.json())
